The evidence with the title 'NRA's home invasion attack ad targeting Missouri Senate ... ' says Sep 9, 2016  ... In 2014 , an NRA ad showed a home invasion while claiming that then-Louisiana sen. Mary Landrieu “ voted to take away your gun rights . ”In that ad, the NRA cited Landrieu 's vote in favor of expanding background checks on gun sales following the 2012 Sandy Hook Elementary School mass shooting . 
